---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Crystal Group"
  description="Learn how Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd collects, uses, and protects your personal data on crystalgroup.in."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-secondary pt-32 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-[860px]">
      <span class="font-body font-bold text-eyebrow uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-4 block">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h1 text-primary leading-tight tracking-tighter">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-primary/40 mt-3">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="bg-primary py-16 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-[860px] font-body">

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 first:border-0 first:pt-0 first:mt-0">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd ("Crystal Group", "we", "us") operates crystalgroup.in. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you visit our website or interact with our services.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        By using our website, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. We are committed to handling your data responsibly and transparently.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We collect information you provide directly, as well as data gathered automatically through your use of the website:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Contact form submissions — name, email address, phone number, company name, and message content</li>
        <li>Website usage data via Google Analytics 4 and Microsoft Clarity — anonymised IP address, pages visited, and session duration</li>
        <li>Enquiry and quote request details submitted through our site</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The information we collect is used solely to serve you and improve our offerings:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Responding to your enquiries and providing quotes for our services</li>
        <li>Improving our website experience and the quality of our services</li>
        <li>Sending relevant updates and communications — only with your explicit consent</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal data to third parties for marketing or any other commercial purpose.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our website uses cookies to enhance your experience and to understand how visitors use our site:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Essential cookies — required for basic site functionality and cannot be disabled</li>
        <li>Analytics cookies — used by Google Analytics 4 and Microsoft Clarity to collect anonymised usage data; you may opt out by adjusting your browser settings</li>
        <li>We do not use advertising or third-party tracking cookies</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We take the security of your data seriously and maintain appropriate technical and organisational safeguards:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>All data is stored on secure servers located in India</li>
        <li>Contact form submissions are retained for a maximum of 24 months</li>
        <li>Analytics data is retained in accordance with Google and Microsoft's respective data retention policies</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        You have the following rights with respect to your personal data:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-md text-secondary/70 mb-4 ml-4">
        <li>Access, correct, or request deletion of your personal data at any time</li>
        <li>Opt out of analytics data collection by adjusting your browser settings or using an ad blocker</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for communications at any time by contacting us directly</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:marketing@crystalgroup.in" class="text-accent hover:underline">marketing@crystalgroup.in</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-h3 text-secondary tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 pt-10 border-t border-secondary/10">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please reach out to us:
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-1">Crystal Logistic Cool Chain Ltd</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-1">601 Synergy Business Park, Sahakar Road</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-1">Off Aarey Road, Goregaon East</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">Mumbai, Maharashtra 400063</p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Email: <a href="mailto:marketing@crystalgroup.in" class="text-accent hover:underline">marketing@crystalgroup.in</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
